des: The LSAT is the first step on the path to legal education and a career in the world of law, and LSAC has been administering the test for more than 70 years. We'll help you learn how to register and prepare for the test, keep you informed of upcoming test dates and other opportunities, and share some of the things you can do with a law degree. We hope you'll join LSAC in our goal of opening the doors of justice to all who seek it — and, in turn, creating a more just and prosperous world.
